Blood Malediction					KEY:Blood Hunter ~ Blood Malediction								CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Blood Hunter a07a	TYPE:Blood Hunter Class Feature.Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.3	DESC:At 2nd level, you gain the knowledge to further channel, and sacrifice, a part of your vital essence to curse and manipulate your enemies. You gain two blood curses of your choice. detailed in the "blood curses" section below. You learn one additional blood curse of your choice at 9th, 13th, and 17th level. When you use your Blood Maledict, you choose which curse to invoke. While invoking a blood curse, but before it affects the target, you may choose to ampily the curse by suffering damage equal to your crimson rite damage die. An amplified curse gains an additional effect, noted in the curse's description. Creatures that do not have blood in their bodies are immune to blood curses (DM's discretion). You can use this feature twice. You regain expended uses when you finish a short or long rest. Beginning at 6th level, you can use your Blood Maledict two times between rests, at 11th level you can use it three times between rests, and at 17th level, you can use it four times between rests.	BONUS:VAR|POOL_BloodHunterBloodCurse|1+(BloodHunterLVL>=5)+(BloodHunterLVL>=9)+(BloodHunterLVL>=13)+(BloodHunterLVL>=16)+(BloodHunterLVL>=20)	DEFINE:POOL_BloodHunterBloodCurse|0	DEFINE:BloodMaledictionTimes|0	BONUS:VAR|BloodMaledictionTimes|1+(BloodHunterLVL>=6)+(BloodHunterLVL>=11)+(BloodHunterLVL>=17)	ASPECT:NAME|Blood Malediction (%1/Rest)|BloodMaledictionTimes
Blood Hunter Order				KEY:Blood Hunter ~ Blood Hunter Order								CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Blood Hunter a04a	TYPE:Blood Hunter Class Feature.Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:At 3rd level, you commit to an order of blood hunter martial focus. Choose Order of the Mutant, Order of the Ghostslayer, or Order of the Profane Soul, all detailed at the end of the class description. The order you choose grants you features at 3rd level, and again at 7th, 11th, 15th, and 18th level.	DEFINE:POOL_BloodHunterOrder|0	BONUS:VAR|POOL_BloodHunterOrder|1
Ability Score Improvement			KEY:Blood Hunter ~ Ability Score Improvement							CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Blood Hunter a05a	TYPE:Blood Hunter Class Feature.Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:When you reach 4th level, and again at 8th, 12th, 16th, and 19th level, you can increase one ability score of your choice by 2, or you can increase two ability scores of your choice by 1. As normal, you can't increase an ability score above 20 using this feature.																																																																																																																																																																																																																								BONUS:VAR|POOL_Character_Advancement_Selection|2*((BloodHunterLVL>=4)+(BloodHunterLVL>=8)+(BloodHunterLVL>=12)+(BloodHunterLVL>=16)+(BloodHunterLVL>=19))
