Formulas					KEY:Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant ~ Formulas							CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Blood Hunter a04c	TYPE:Blood Hunter Class Feature.Class Feature.Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant.Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant Lvl 03.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:You begin to uncover forbidden alchemical formulas that temporarily alter your mental and physical abilities. Beginning at 3rd level, you choose to learn three mutagen formulas. Your formula options are detailed at the end of this order description. You gain an additional formula at 7th level, 10th level, 13th level, 15th level, and 20th level. Additionally, when you gain a mutagen formula at levels 7. 10, 13, 15, and 20, you can choose one of the formulas you know and replace it with another mutagen formula.	DEFINE:POOL_BloodHunterMutagen|0	BONUS:VAR|POOL_BloodHunterMutagen|3+(BloodHunterLVL>=7)+(BloodHunterLVL>=10)+(BloodHunterLVL>=13)+(BloodHunterLVL>=15)+(BloodHunterLVL>=20)
Mutagen Craft				KEY:Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant ~ Mutagen Craft						CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Blood Hunter a04c	TYPE:Blood Hunter Class Feature.Class Feature.Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant.Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant Lvl 03.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:At 3rd level, you can take a short rest to concoct a single mutagen. Consuming a single mutagen requires a bonus action, and the effects (including side effects) last until you finish another short or long rest. Mutagens are designed for your biology and are fatal to anyone who consumes one other than you. Mutagens are unstable by nature, losing their potency over time and becoming inert if not used before you finish your next short or long rest.
Advanced Mutagen Craft			KEY:Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant ~ Advanced Mutagen Craft				CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Blood Hunter a04c	TYPE:Blood Hunter Class Feature.Class Feature.Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant.Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant Lvl 07.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:Upon reaching 7th level, when you take a short rest to concoct a mutagen, you can now create two. Mutagens must be different formulas, and can be ingested with overlapping effects that last until you finish your next short or long rest. Each mutagen still takes a separate bonus action to imbibe. Once you reach 15th level, you can now create three mutagens during a short rest.
Strange Metabolism			KEY:Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant ~ Strange Metabolism					CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Blood Hunter a04c	TYPE:Blood Hunter Class Feature.Class Feature.Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant.Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant Lvl 11.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:Beginning at 11th level, you can use a bonus action to instill a burst of adrenaline to temporarily resist the negative effects of a mutagen. You can choose to ignore the side effect of a mutagen affecting you for 1 minute. Once you use this feature, you must finish a short or long rest before you can use it again.
Robust Physiology				KEY:Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant ~ Robust Physiology					CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Blood Hunter a04c	TYPE:Blood Hunter Class Feature.Class Feature.Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant.Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant Lvl 15.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:At l5th level, your body has begun to adapt to toxins and venoms, ignoring their corroding effects. You gain immunity to poison damage and the poisoned condition.
Exalted Mutation				KEY:Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant ~ Exalted Mutation					CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Blood Hunter a04c	TYPE:Blood Hunter Class Feature.Class Feature.Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant.Blood Hunter Order Of The Mutant Lvl 18.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:At 18th level, your body has begun producing one of your toxins naturally. Choose one of your known mutagen formulas. You gain the benefits and side effects of this mutagen permanently, at all times. You cannot change this choice of forumla after this feature is acquired.

